name: ANA 787-8 "Dreamliner" landing at Paine Field [HD]
description:
Hello everyone, this is an All Nippon Airways Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner landing at Paine Field (KPAE/PAE) after a short test flight. The landing would have been pretty smooth had he not bounced. I hope you enjoy :)

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
